template

public java.lang.String template
The template which is used for rendering of projection variable results for a single binding set example: - SELECT ?a ?b WHERE { .. } - Bindings: {{?a=A1,?b=B1}, {?a=A2,?b=B2}} - Template: "{{{a}}} {{{b}}})" Result: (A1 - B1) separator (A2 - B2) ... Default: Projection variables are comma separated
